properties.Title: Bilkent University
properties.City: This was the caption of my instagram post on 26th September 2014 in a lab using an oscillisocope for the first time at Bilkent University. Though there has been sleeples nights in those labs throughout four years of my Bachelors degree, the feeling when I received my Bachelor of Science degree is indescribable. Graduating with an honors degree was of course a source of joy and satisfaction, but more, much more than this I did it my way!
